libflv version 0.1. 

In order to use libflv you need zlib header-files and .so files installed. 
Compile:
	cd src/
	make 
Install:
	set LIBDIR and INCLUDEDIR as you like
	make install (as root)

In order to use the library #include <libflv.h> and link your program with -lflv.


For examples and documentation visit: http://klaus.geekserver.net/libflv/
If you find bugs or have sugestions please mail to: klaus{At}rechert.de.

26.7.2004
